OL,7,G1,000 members of the National Union
OL,8,Gof Journalists working at BBC Local
OL,9,Ghave started a 48-hour strike, in
OL,10,Gopposition to cuts to programming and
OL,11,Gstaffing at local radio stations in
OL,12,GEngland.
OL,14,FThe strike has caused significant
OL,15,Fdisruption to local BBC TV, radio and
OL,16,Fonline services across England.
OL,18,FA 24-hour strike in March took all
OL,19,Fbut two regional TV services off the
OL,20,Fair and severely impacted local radio
OL,21,Foutput and online services.
OL,3,CLocal BBC TV, radio and online
OL,4,Cservices in England hit by strike
OL,5,Caction
