OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F352A1688309604
OL,7,FThe BBC claims the audience for BBC
OL,8,Flocal radio is in decline and that
OL,9,Fthere are more effective ways of
OL,10,Fserving local audiences. To that end,
OL,11,Fthe BBC intends to invest in
OL,12,Fenhancing digital offerings such as
OL,13,Flocal journalism on the BBC News
OL,14,Fwebsite.
OL,16,FThe BBC's plan for local radio will
OL,17,Fsee some stations sharing the same
OL,18,Fprogramming from early afternoon
OL,19,Funtil late-evening. The changes will
OL,20,Fresult in the departure of many
OL,21,Flongstanding familiar voices at local
OL,22,Fstations.
OL,3,CLocal BBC TV, radio and online
