PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F352A1688309604
OL,7,F"Two ballots were held to gauge the
OL,8,Fmood of NUJ members in BBC Local
OL,9,Fduring this period. They made it
OL,10,Fclear that the revised plan was
OL,11,Funacceptable and voted overwhelmingly
OL,12,Ffor industrial action.
OL,14,F"We held back on strike action
OL,15,Fbecause we hoped the Senior Leaders
OL,16,Fwould listen to not only our views,
OL,17,Fbut those of the listeners, MPs, and
OL,18,Findustry experts who all said the
OL,19,Fproposals were deeply flawed.
OL,3,CLocal BBC TV, radio and online
OL,4,Cservices in England hit by strike
